OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: Recognising
OL,4,Cearly baby loss
OL,6,FWhen a pregnancy ends and a baby is
OL,7,Flost, it can be traumatic and
OL,8,Fdevastating.
OL,10,FBut Kelly Barnes experienced 11 failed
OL,11,Fpregnancies in the space of only a few
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FHer loss led her down a path where she
OL,15,Fnot only helps others through her work
OL,16,Fwith Sands, the charity which helps
OL,17,Fpeople affected by the loss of a baby
OL,18,Fbut she also campaigned for the
OL,19,Fintroduction of a formal baby loss
OL,20,Fcertificate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
