OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784761381
OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: Recognising
OL,4,Cearly baby loss
OL,6,FAfter a long consultation, this scheme
OL,7,Fwas introduced last month.
OL,9,FFor Kelly she sees the benefit of the
OL,10,Fcertificate in three ways. Firstly,
OL,11,Fwhile it's not a legal document, it is
OL,12,Fan acknowledgement that even for a
OL,13,Fshort time, that baby existed.
OL,15,FIt might seem innocuous but many women
OL,16,Fgo through miscarriage privately, and
OL,17,Fthis might be one of the only ways of
OL,18,Frecognising the loss of a pregnancy.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
