PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784761381
OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: Recognising
OL,4,Cearly baby loss
OL,6,FAs Kelly says, as soon as a woman sees
OL,7,Fthat positive test, that baby is a
OL,8,Fbeing. It figures in plans and dreams.
OL,10,FThe baby loss certificate is also a
OL,11,Fmeans to starting a conversation. This
OL,12,Fis a conversation which Kelly says
OL,13,Fneeds to be normalised.
OL,15,FBaby loss is a hugely sensitive topic
OL,16,Fand one which many are nervous to
OL,17,Fapproach.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784761381
OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: Recognising
OL,4,Cearly baby loss
OL,6,FBut for Kelly, she says she loved
OL,7,Fevery one of her babies and like other
OL,8,Fmums, she wants to talk about them.
OL,9,FShe says avoiding the topic and not
OL,10,Facknowledging the loss is more harmful
OL,11,Fthat starting the conversation.
OL,13,FThirdly, Kelly feels that the
OL,14,Fcertificates can actually kickstart
OL,15,Fthe grieving process, even for those
OL,16,Fwho have lost babies in early
OL,17,Fpregnancy.
OL,19,FShe's keen to emphasise that loss is
OL,20,Floss, be it six weeks or twenty. And
OL,21,Feach loss can be a trauma.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
